Package: gaplightr
Title: Gap Light Analysis of Virtual and Real Fisheye Photography
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    c(person("Gord", "Frazer", email = "gordonwfrazer@gmail.com", role = "aut", comment = "Conceptualization and original code"),
    person("Sam", "Albers", email = "sam.albers@hakai.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Hakai Institute", , role = "cph"))
Description: Analyzes forest canopy gap light transmission using LiDAR point cloud
    data and hemispherical photography. Provides tools for processing LiDAR data,
    computing horizon angles, and calculating gap light metrics.
